skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: starship enterprise
des: Ozzy Trek was designed for all your audio Trekkie needs. Like being on the USS Enterprise. The ship is outfitted with the following: Shields, Cloak, Phasers, Photon Torpedos, Probes, Tractor Beam, Scanners, Turbolift, Holo Deck, and a Warp Core. You can also try to search the database, run diagnostics, and listen to log files. Security codes may be required. It can also try to beam you aboard. There is even an auto slash self destruct in case you get into trouble.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
